  "SET UP A-IVI2 TIME": {
   "width": 13620,
   "height": 8998,
   "color": "rgb(133,156,252)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "A-IVI2 shall perform SET UP A-IVC TIME   following details below.     Organe To be controlled: A-IVI2     Function to be performed: Set A-IVI2 Time     \"Conditions: When this request is sent, the requested time will be set in A-IVI2\" Tool frame request to ECU:     \"Note : For the Read time OptionRecord \"\"$00\"\" the other bytes should be sent with 00 pading \"\"000000000000\"\" Read time : 31  01  870B 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 Write time :  31  01  870B 01  XX XX XX XX XX XX\"",
