     "text": "A-IVI2 shall reset FOTA State Machine following details below.     Organe To be controlled: A-IVI2,       Function to be performed:      When the routine is launched the A-IVI2  must reset the FOTA service. It means:     -\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Reset AIVI FOTA State Machines incl SWMC to ensure to restart from an Idle state     -\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Erase FOTA buffer          Conditions: VIN is already set in A-IVI2 ",
