   "width": 13620,
   "height": 8204,
   "color": "rgb(133,156,252)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "A-IVI2 shall add or remove a sheltered parameter with this routine. Means that those parameter values will be protected or unprotected from $2E overwriting request coming from coding strings defined in F-A01-15_A-IVI2_OTA_Configuration.  Those protected parameters can still be overwritten through $2E request coming from DoIP local tester.  Organe To be controlled: A-IVI2,   This is a type 2 routine",
