  "ASSET DAEMON DATA REFERENCE": {
   "width": 13620,
   "height": 11302,
   "color": "rgb(133,156,252)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "A-IVI2 shall perform  ASSET DAEMON DATA REFERENCE  routine defined below.  Organe To be controlled: A-IVI2 Function to be performed: 1. start the routine with the startRoutine sub-function 2. call the requestRoutineResults sub-function  if the response contains routineInfo = routineActive, the information in routineStatus is irrelevant  the tool must call requestRoutineResults  if the response contains routineInfo = routineCompleted, the information in routineStatus contains the references of the assets in / data  the tool must call stopRoutine 3. call stop routine when requestRoutineResults returns routineCompleted with a pertinet routineStatus. ",
     "color": "rgb(255,128,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 960,
      "top": 120,
      "height": 4632,
      "width": 12120
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MV Boli",
      "size": 11.0,
