   "width": 13620,
   "height": 8262,
   "color": "rgb(133,156,252)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "AIVI2 shall perform the CONFIGURATION HASH routine as defined below : Organe to be controlled: AIVI2 Function to be performed: This routine shall be equivalent to pa_helper 3 and 8 (adb shell pa_helper 3 sit/stg/prd) : the idea is to set recovery, FOTA and rootCA keys  Technical limitation : not able to restore full crypto backup (provionning done by supplier). Update will work but routine not enough for PA  Restriction : shall be used only on none secure HW, need to get device HW security information  ",
