  "CONTROL TUNER SETTINGS": {
   "width": 13620,
   "height": 10228,
   "color": "rgb(133,156,252)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "A-IVI2 shall implement I/O control service ($2F) according to [1] and [2] to perform tuner settings following details below  Organe To be controlled: Radio tuners When ECU receives this request, it will load tuner settings. Positive response will be issued when parameters are taken into account by tuner. Tuner keeps the settings after end of test.  The frequency step and range are dependent of the geographic area choose on the configuration setting.  Conditions: Antennas must be fitted",
     "color": "rgb(255,128,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
