     "text": "Example\u00a0:100.3 MHz    --> $20 31 30 30 33 Set the tuner to this frequency If the frequency is out of range for the specified band, a negative response is issued. If digital radio band, set the tuner to this channel number. and find the first service in this channel 585 KHz  --> $20 20 35 38 35 CN12D --> $43 4E 31 32 44  Test is temporary. It will stop by itself.",
