  "CONTROL LOUDSPEAKERS TONE": {
   "width": 13620,
   "height": 19620,
   "color": "rgb(133,156,252)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "A-IVI2 shall implement I/O control service ($2F) according to [1] and [2] to perform loudspeakers tone following the details below :  Organe To be controlled: loudspeakers  By using this request, ECU should be able to issue a tone following loudspeaker line number, frequency and sound level given as parameters. When a tone is requested, ECU must:  Mute all sources  Issue the requested tone  Return to normal state It must not be possible to issue a tone to more than one (1) loudspeaker Conditions: loudspeakers must be fitted  A-IVI2 shall Start the Control of loudspeakers tone, when it receives the order with I/O Control Option Record at $03 (Short Term Adjustment) .  A-IVI2 shall Stop the Control of loudspeakers tone, when it receives the order with I/O Control Option Record at $00 (Return Control to ECU) .  A-IVI2 shall Stop the Control of loudspeakers tone if no $00 (Return Control to ECU) is sent after 20 seconds. ",
     "color": "rgb(255,128,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
