  "GRAPHIC DISPLAY TEST": {
   "width": 13620,
   "height": 11174,
   "color": "rgb(133,156,252)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "A-IVI2 shall implement I/O control service ($2F) according to [1] and [2] to perform Graphic display test following details below  Organe To be controlled: Graphic screen  When requested by diagnosis tool, A-IVI must display black or white screen.  Conditions : External screen must be fitted  A-IVI2  shall Start the Control of Graphic display test, when it receives the order with I/O Control Option Record at $03 (Short Term Adjustment).  A-IVI2  shall Stop the Control of Graphic display test, when it receives the order with I/O Control Option Record at $00 (Return Control to ECU).  A-IVI2  shall Stop the Control of Graphic display test if no $00 (Return Control to ECU) is sent after 20 seconds according to [Diag-940]e & [Diag -920]a  ",
     "color": "rgb(255,128,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
