  "PERFORM SPEAKER TEST": {
   "width": 13620,
   "height": 8116,
   "color": "rgb(133,156,252)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "A-IVI2  shall implement I/O control service ($2F) according to [1] and [2] to perform speaker test following details below Organe To be controlled:  By using this request, ECU should be able to perform a specific test in order to detect whether each speaker is correctly connected or not. The IO control is temporary. The IO control lasts around 10 seconds and cannot be stop before completion. This I/O control should trigger the test of all loudspeaker & tweeters open load DTC that can not be done continuously   Conditions:  A-IVI2  shall Start the Control of SpeakerTest, when it receives the order with I/O Control Option Record at $03 (Short Term Adjustment) according to [Diag-970].   A-IVI2 shall Stop the Control of speaker test automatically.",
     "color": "rgb(255,128,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
